wiki.content: “Beat The Odds” marks as Lil Tjay’s first song after recovering from injuries due to a rivalry shooting. Throughout the song, he raps about his past life and mentions family members who have been there for him since his young days, also leading over to his gang affiliations, selecting murder as his choice. On August 24, 2022, Tjay uploaded an Instagram video expressing his love for his fans, and showing support after his near-death experience. In the caption, he states: "Thanks for the love and support ya I appreciate everything fr… 🫶🏾we gon come back stronger than ever ‼️‼️ ya ready 👀👀👀" Hours prior the release, he revealed the cover art of the song, along with the caption: "BEAT DA ODDS TONIGHT @ MIDNIGHT … 🖤🙏🏾" Read more on Last.fm.
